{"tid":721784,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"點解做齊曬所有護膚步驟仲會生暗瘡?","createTime":"2018-06-29T02:40:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T03:28:25.000Z","uid":137912,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fdd712acae46fc29e494fa02d8270f4100cfd775","tid":721784,"uid":137912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:40:25.000Z","msg":"我每日都會做護膚三步曲<br />\n<br />\n1. 潔面<br />\n<br />\n我用曼秀西敦暗瘡護理潔面乳洗面 每次洗面都會係生暗瘡嘅位捽耐啲<br />\n<br />\n2. 爽膚<br />\n<br />\n我每日都會濕啲eaude muge 藥用化妝水落棉花到 之後再抹面<br />\n<br />\n3. 保濕<br />\n<br />\n爽完膚之後我會用Water360礦泉臻潤水珠倍潤霜保濕 啲sales話依個零油份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講番自己皮膚狀況<br />\nT字位偶有暗瘡<br />\n鼻翼兩邊仍有<br />\n下巴勁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇全能嘅連燈仔可以幫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4a2618c4fb2e014a36caee2a91efbc7bcf889a","tid":721784,"uid":54076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:47:08.000Z","msg":"下巴多係腸胃唔好 靠洗面唔夠 要控制飲食 早睡早起<br />\n利申：9up"},{"pid":"d01d66263b673a0d508f026a0b85246597a4959a","tid":721784,"uid":156652,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:48:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://viso.com.hk/image/cache/data/Clip/Calbee/hotspicy%20105g-600x600_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fviso.com.hk%2Fimage%2Fcache%2Fdata%2FClip%2FCalbee%2Fhotspicy%2520105g-600x600_0.jpg&h=a67896a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"761cae24c51a9cfa845dfd07b1b8a0132371b85d","tid":721784,"uid":81256,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:50:34.000Z","msg":"內分泌<br />\n腸胃健康<br />\n<br />\n先係暗瘡主因<br />\n<br />\n表面清潔只影響10%<br />\n<br />\n我建議睇中醫調理<br />\n日常做運動，早睡早起，好緊要<br />\n<br />\n利申：過來人"},{"pid":"b20d4ad99a28b1730406f3f135ca914daf5c5f40","tid":721784,"uid":83798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:50:58.000Z","msg":"你用嘅護膚品唔適合你？護膚品係要狂試先搵到岩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58baaf67c5bf1b55a7a7045ce32d3e62dc425776","tid":721784,"uid":86442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:55:41.000Z","msg":"如果唔係勁油/青春期，其實一日用一次潔面用品就得"},{"pid":"eba54dd8d51353f461ee8357c6c24a0f3e99c6ab","tid":721784,"uid":20845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T03:08:13.000Z","msg":"係護膚品上 洗面唔需要特登某個位置捽耐啲或者大力啲 有時皮膚無左個油分保護 仲容易短時間內出多左油 暗蒼都會多左<br />\n作息上 如果返工少出到汗 就盡量飲多啲水去多幾次廁所 唔好夜訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e96d6ce506bd711eff68e801544d3cc1ef1fd81","tid":721784,"uid":127347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T03:14:26.000Z","msg":"我明白，我都做好晒都係咁爆，暗瘡真係on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53a26bf91ab96fb7c169cc677dd33443d0ad93d3","tid":721784,"uid":8745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T03:24:44.000Z","msg":"生暗瘡有好多原因: 內分泌/皮脂/蟎蟲/壓力...<br />\n<br />\n護膚品唔係藥，係用黎做皮膚日常清潔保養，多數只影響到角質層，極少會去到皮脂腺所在嘅真皮層，不過打理好角質層可以幫助保護真皮層"},{"pid":"163ab467dbd2bea59caf288ca0914afd4a2355d0","tid":721784,"uid":145015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T03:25:40.000Z","msg":"戴套都有機會有bb啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e44150ac878120cdd248d25e00235084ba435b7e","tid":721784,"uid":160431,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T03:26:39.000Z","msg":"打得多飛機鼻既兩邊都會生暗瘡"},{"pid":"1099976169a13b95c03f1db3510ea1e16ee2b193","tid":721784,"uid":181797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T03:28:25.000Z","msg":"基因，空氣，水質"}]}